{"id":589576,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/翻墙广播-习近平标语悄然下架的北京/","date":"2018-07-18T06:57:52Z","modified":"2018-07-18T06:57:52Z","title":"翻墙广播 | “习近平标语”悄然下架的北京","content":"<p>7月3日，湖南女孩<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E7%BD%91%E6%B0%91%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E6%B3%BC%E5%A2%A8%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%83%8F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%AB%E8%91%A3%E7%91%B6%E7%90%BC/\">董瑶琼</a>在上海海航总部前对着巨幅习近平像的勇敢一泼，随即引发了各地效仿，网民用此方式支持被官方带走失联的&#8221;泼墨女孩&#8221;的同时，也为积压已久的不满找到了抒发的出口。</p>\n<p>官方媒体对于“泼墨”一事一如既往的噤若寒蝉，可自从去年十九大前夕遍布北京的“习式”标语却正在悄然下架。</p>\n<p>原本遍布北京人行天桥的十九大或是宣传习近平思想相关标语如今却不见了踪影。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_589580\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/01ec83c2ade443080b6eb.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589580\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/01ec83c2ade443080b6eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/01ec83c2ade443080b6eb.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/01ec83c2ade443080b6eb-300x166.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/01ec83c2ade443080b6eb-768x425.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">挂于北京天桥上的&#8221;习式&#8221;特色标语（摄于2017.10.17 图片来源：东方网）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589581\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589581\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb.jpg 1500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/d0a1ffb96b6de0f3fd2cb-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">位于崇文门附近的人行天桥，往日的标语已不见踪迹（摄于2018.07.14）</p></div>\n<p>而曾经占据了北京大街小巷外墙空间、诸如&#8221;共产党好，百姓乐&#8221;等系列主题宣传画，也正在纯白的新漆或是与政治无关的风景绘画代替。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_589582\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589582\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a.jpg 1050w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a-768x513.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/bcf84bb9666864526504a-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">北京外墙上的&#8221;心向党&#8221;宣传画（图片来源：纽约时报中文网 2018.01.29）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589583\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589583\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a.jpg 1500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a-300x171.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a-768x439.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/ed302b8e5dda2c689491a-1024x585.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">恢复了空白的北京外墙（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589586\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589586\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f.jpg 1246w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f-300x235.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f-768x602.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/464ad33399799921ab92f-1024x803.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">宣传画被白漆抹去（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589587\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589587\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"474\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a.jpg 2933w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a-300x259.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a-768x662.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/1b454f08f4b78f0d1966a-1024x883.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">南三环附近 尚在绘制风景画中外墙（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<p>除此之外，北京党政机关原本悬挂的&#8221;习式标语&#8221;似乎也被悉数撤下。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_589588\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/413a8c5edb82bbe5215c8.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589588\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/413a8c5edb82bbe5215c8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/413a8c5edb82bbe5215c8.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/413a8c5edb82bbe5215c8-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/413a8c5edb82bbe5215c8-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">北京卫戍区空军总部门前，未悬挂任何宣传标语（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589590\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a9c388f0d2875a3e0a96f.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589590\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a9c388f0d2875a3e0a96f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a9c388f0d2875a3e0a96f.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a9c388f0d2875a3e0a96f-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">北京市工商联大厦（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_589591\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a17f6d9c3744538207a32.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589591\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a17f6d9c3744538207a32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a17f6d9c3744538207a32.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/a17f6d9c3744538207a32-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">北京古城墙附近，框内原本架托着的&#8221;富强&#8221;&#8221;民主&#8221;&#8221;文明&#8221;等由习近平提出的社会主义核心价值观字眼，也被悄悄摘除了（摄于2018.07.15）</p></div>\n<p>中共北戴河会议召开在即，而北京此时却正在悄悄撤下带有习近平色彩的标语或横幅，其原因究竟是中共老人集体施压习近平，其目前已经失去实际权力所致，还是习本人震怒于全国对于其画像或标语的泼墨举动，并害怕此事愈演愈烈，因此做出了撤下相关标语的指示，亦或是出于其他原因，我们不得而知，然而此时这样的举动无疑给原本就扑朔迷离的真相又蒙上了一层迷雾。中国政治究竟会是怎样的走向，答案只能等待时间来揭晓了。</p>\n<p>翻墙广播<a href=\"https://t.me/fanqiangguangbo\">电报频道</a></p>\n<p>中国数字时代<a href=\"https://t.me/cdtchinesefeed\">电报频道</a></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\">习近平个人崇拜</a></strong></p>\n<pre><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91%e6%b3%bc%e5%a2%a8%e4%b9%8b%e5%90%8e%e6%80%8e%e6%a0%b7%ef%bc%9f%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%8b%e5%8f%88%e6%9c%89%e5%a5%87%e6%80%9d%e5%a6%99%e6%83%b3%ef%bc%81/\">【众人推】泼墨之后怎样？网友又有奇思妙想！</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"【立此存照】华涌与董建彪推特发布声明\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%8d%8e%e6%b6%8c%e4%b8%8e%e8%91%a3%e5%bb%ba%e5%bd%aa%e6%8e%a8%e7%89%b9%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e5%a3%b0%e6%98%8e/\">【立此存照】华涌与董建彪推特发布声明</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"【立此存照】关于规范户外公益广告的通知\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%85%b3%e4%ba%8e%e8%a7%84%e8%8c%83%e6%88%b7%e5%a4%96%e5%85%ac%e7%9b%8a%e5%b9%bf%e5%91%8a%e7%9a%84%e9%80%9a%e7%9f%a5/\">【立此存照】关于规范户外公益广告的通知</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"自由亚洲 | 墨攻奏效？京城撤习近平照片、海报\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e4%ba%9a%e6%b4%b2-%e5%a2%a8%e6%94%bb%e5%a5%8f%e6%95%88%ef%bc%9f%e4%ba%ac%e5%9f%8e%e6%92%a4%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e7%85%a7%e7%89%87%e3%80%81%e6%b5%b7%e6%8a%a5/\">自由亚洲 | 墨攻奏效？京城撤习近平照片、海报</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"【立此存照】立即撤下习近平同志画像\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%ab%8b%e5%8d%b3%e6%92%a4%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%a0%e8%bf%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%90%8c%e5%bf%97%e7%94%bb%e5%83%8f/\">【立此存照】立即撤下习近平同志画像</a></pre>\n</blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,20534],"tags":[27046,35274,27274,35273,13222,33609,32609,13335,31040,33491,35217,26276,33484,35275]}